  "body": "Similar to #718, #1185. In this case, we want PR that can successfully transition through different epochs. This would allow us to have high confidence in our runtime if epoch transitions can execute flawlessly from a YAML test.\r\n\r\nA follow-up PR can implement better debugging tools and perhaps a dump of the state at the beginning of each epoch to visualize: \r\n1.) validator status, balances and who has been rewarded/penalized \r\n2.) current justification and finalization status of previous epoch slots",
